<div class="container">
<div class="well">
	<h3>如何链接矿池</h3>
	<hr>
	<h4>1. 选择矿池服务器和端口:</h4>
	<div class="table-responsive">
		<table class="table table-condensed table-bordered">
		<tbody>
		<tr class="text-center">
			<th class="text-right">
				Server
			</th>
			<td>
				eth.3pool.cn
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr class="text-center">
			<th class="text-right">
				Stratum Port
			</th>
			<td colspan="4">
				9999
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr class="text-center">
			<th class="text-right">
				Http Port
			</th>
			<td colspan="4">
				9009
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr class="text-center">
			<th class="text-right">
				Username
			</th>
			<td colspan="4">
				你的以太坊钱包地址,例如:0xb85150eb365e7df0941f0cf08235f987ba91506a
			</td>
		</tr>
		</tbody>
		</table>
	</div>
	<h4>2. 选择你的挖矿软件: </h4>
	<ul role="tablist" class="nav nav-tabs">
		<li role="presentation" class="active"><a href="#Claymore" aria-controls="Claymore" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">Claymore</a></li>
		<li role="presentation"><a href="#Ethminer" aria-controls="Ethminer" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">Ethminer</a></li>
		<li role="presentation"><a href="#EthProxy" aria-controls="EthProxy" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">Eth Proxy</a></li>
	</ul>
	<div class="tab-content">
		<div role="tabpanel" id="Claymore" class="tab-pane active">
			<div class="panel panel-default">
				<div class="panel-body">
					<h5>下载,配置和运行Claymore miner</h5>
					<ul>
						<li>下载和配置教程: <a href="https://github.com/nanopool/Claymore-Dual-Miner" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Github</a></li>
					</ul>
					<h5>使用以下命令启动挖矿,将你的以太坊钱包地址做为用户名</h5>
					<pre>ethdcrminer64.exe -epool eth.3pool.cn:9999 -ewal 以太坊钱包地址 -epsw 密码 -eworker 矿工名</pre>
					<h5>完整命令实例</h5>
					<pre>ethdcrminer64.exe -epool eth.3pool.cn:9999 -ewal 0xb85150eb365e7df0941f0cf08235f987ba91506a -epsw x -eworker rig-1</pre>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div role="tabpanel" id="Ethminer" class="tab-pane">
			<div class="panel panel-default">
				<div class="panel-body">
					<h5>下载,配置和运行Ethminer</h5>
					<ul>
						<li>下载和配置教程: <a href="https://github.com/ethereum-mining/ethminer/releases" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Github</a></li>
					</ul>
					<h5>使用以下命令启动挖矿,将你的以太坊钱包地址做为用户名</h5>
					<pre>setx GPU_FORCE_64BIT_PTR 0
setx GPU_MAX_HEAP_SIZE 100
setx GPU_USE_SYNC_OBJECTS 1
setx GPU_MAX_ALLOC_PERCENT 100
setx GPU_SINGLE_ALLOC_PERCENT 100
ethminer.exe --farm-recheck 200 -G -S eth.3pool.cn:9999 -O 以太坊钱包地址.矿工名</pre>
					<h5>完整命令实例</h5>
					<pre>setx GPU_FORCE_64BIT_PTR 0
setx GPU_MAX_HEAP_SIZE 100
setx GPU_USE_SYNC_OBJECTS 1
setx GPU_MAX_ALLOC_PERCENT 100
setx GPU_SINGLE_ALLOC_PERCENT 100
ethminer.exe --farm-recheck 200 -G -S eth.3pool.cn:9999 -O 0xb85150eb365e7df0941f0cf08235f987ba91506a.rig-1</pre>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div role="tabpanel" id="EthProxy" class="tab-pane">
			<div class="panel panel-default">
				<div class="panel-body">
					<h5>下载,配置和运行Eth Proxy</h5>
					<ul>
						<li>下载和配置教程: <a href="https://github.com/Atrides/eth-proxy" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Github</a></li>
					</ul>
					<h5>修改eth-proxy.conf配置文件内容,将你的以太坊钱包地址做为用户名</h5>
					<h5>完整命令实例</h5>
					<pre>COIN = "ETH"
HOST = "127.0.0.1"
PORT = 8080
# 将下面的地址改成你的钱包地址,用来接受挖到的币
WALLET = "0xb85150eb365e7df0941f0cf08235f987ba91506a"
# 给矿机设置编号
ENABLE_WORKER_ID = True 
# 主矿池
POOL_HOST = "eth.3pool.cn"
POOL_PORT = 9999
# 备用矿池
POOL_FAILOVER_ENABLE = True
POOL_HOST_FAILOVER1 = "eth.3pool.cn"
POOL_PORT_FAILOVER1 = 9009
LOG_TO_FILE = True
DEBUG = False</pre>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	</div>
</div>
